fulltitle: Ask the King Ep. 81: May 7, 2020 pt2 - DSP Tries It, Liking to See Me Fail, Console Launches
title: Ask the King Ep. 81: May 7, 2020 pt2 - DSP Tries It, Liking to See Me Fail, Console Launches
description:
Post up your questions for the next episode of Ask the King here: https://thekingofhate.com/forums/topic/5272-ask-the-king-ep-82-july-9-2020/


Topics in this part:
1:05 Have I thought about taking 2 days a week off instead of just one?
5:07 Why did I end DSP Tries It? Would I ever resume it?
11:00 Thinking about trolls actually being a part of my revenue and if I "Defeat" them will that hurt me?
17:00 How tough is it to appease people who are only watching your content for fails or "the LOLz"?
20:45 Thoughts on the new upcoming console launches and if they'll suffer from previous woes from other past launched?
PLUS lots of Twitter and stream chat questions!


And then, live stream questions.
